{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01PyVtjSLAz3Ekfpx7rt3T18","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The issue is clear:\n1. Pod 0 is running but not Ready because its readiness probe is failing with 503. CockroachDB needs `cockroach init` to be run after the cluster is started to initialize the cluster.\n2. But also, StatefulSet only created 1 pod (pod 0), which is normal because StatefulSets by default wait for each pod to become Ready before creating the next one. Since pod 0 is not Ready, pods 1 and 2 won't be created.\n\nThe problem is a chicken-and-egg situation:\n- Pod 0 can't become Ready until the cluster is initialized\n- The cluster can't be initialized until all 3 pods are running\n- Pods 1 and 2 won't start until pod 0 is Ready\n\nThe fix is to switch the StatefulSet to use parallel pod management so all three pods launch simultaneously, then I can run the initialization command once they're all up.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1490,"cache_read_input_tokens":32185,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1490},"output_tokens":21,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"57feb0c6-f11a-4e5d-a4d7-79f6638dafdd","uuid":"36a53ae7-dcdd-410a-9583-fb066b337284","request_id":"req_011CccDnp4xGv5kCEDyC4zmi"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01PyVtjSLAz3Ekfpx7rt3T18","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The issue is a chicken-and-egg: StatefulSet waits for pod 0 to be Ready before creating pods 1 and 2, but pod 0 can't become Ready until `cockroach init` is run, which requires all nodes to be up. The fix is `podManagementPolicy: Parallel`."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1490,"cache_read_input_tokens":32185,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1490},"output_tokens":21,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"57feb0c6-f11a-4e5d-a4d7-79f6638dafdd","uuid":"f2b466b1-af53-4f0f-a89e-c46dc4f32505","request_id":"req_011CccDnp4xGv5kCEDyC4zmi"}
